apps/propertytoolsai/tmp/
apps/propertytoolsai/ml/valuation/artifacts/

# Claude Code local working directory.
#
# `.claude/worktrees/` holds sibling git worktrees (one per
# Claude Code session), each a full checkout of a different
# branch. EAS Build's tar step choked on these because the
# worktree contents reference files that don't exist in the
# current checkout's index — "tar: ... Cannot open: No such
# file or directory" flooded PREPARE_PROJECT and errored the
# build. `.claude/` has no business in a production bundle, so
# exclude the whole directory.
.claude/
